> >|> When I was in the US-Navy (as a peon-class crypto-clerk) I heard of a
> >|> form of "rice paper" used by some spies.
> >|> 

Also available from Magic Stores as 'dissolving paper
 

it turns into mush in about 2-3 seconds tops (assuming you agitate it)
otherwise it will sit in the water, turn into gel, and the next person to 
try and touch it will watch it ooze between their fingers. 


Oddly enough the paper I have feels like a strong bond, not flimsy like 
computer paper, or thinner stock.

